    48â†’## [17.2.0](https://github.com/motdotla/dotenv/compare/v17.1.0...v17.2.0) (2025-07-09)
    49â†’
    50â†’### Added
    51â†’
    52â†’* Optionally specify `DOTENV_CONFIG_QUIET=true` in your environment or `.env` file to quiet the runtime log ([#889](https://github.com/motdotla/dotenv/pull/889))
    53â†’* Just like dotenv any `DOTENV_CONFIG_` environment variables take precedence over any code set options like `({quiet: false})`
    54â†’
    55â†’```ini
    56â†’# .env
    57â†’DOTENV_CONFIG_QUIET=true
    58â†’HELLO="World"
    59â†’```
    60â†’```js
    61â†’// index.js
    62â†’require('dotenv').config()
    63â†’console.log(`Hello ${process.env.HELLO}`)
    64â†’```
    65â†’```sh
    66â†’$ node index.js
    67â†’Hello World
    68â†’
    69â†’or
    70â†’
    71â†’$ DOTENV_CONFIG_QUIET=true node index.js
    72â†’```
    73â†’
    74â†’## [17.1.0](https://github.com/motdotla/dotenv/compare/v17.0.1...v17.1.0) (2025-07-07)
